title: ERA MSS reference monitoring transponders
agents: snmp
author: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH <info@kuhn-ruess.de>
license: GPL
distribution: none
description:
 Reads the rmtrTable (OID .1.3.6.1.4.1.11588.1.5.104) and creates one service
 per reference monitoring transponder. The service reports rmtrStatus as the
 Checkmk state via the common ERA status map.

item:
 Transponder site name (rmtrSiteName).

inventory:
 One service per RMTR with a non-empty site name.
